b'Sherry A. Falsetti, PhD, assistant dean of research, professor and director, Division of Health Policy & Social Science Research, Department of Family and Community Medicine. \xc2\xa0Dr. Falsetti provides overall direction to the Office of Research and administers the programs and internal grant funding mechanisms of the Office. \xc2\xa0She also chairs the James Scholar Program. E:\xc2\xa0falsetti@uic.edu Tel: 815 395.5665Lori Dredske, administrative aide/research coordinator. Lori coordinates the Office of Research programs, grant funding mechanisms and provides administrative support for the Office. E:lorindah@uic.edu Tel: 815 395.5733'
b'falsetti@uic.edu'
b'lorindah@uic.edu'
